
                          Plotser
                          
              Real-time plotting of serial data


    ~ What is it?
      
      Plotser reads data from a serial device and plots it in real-time.
      
    ~ What do I need?
      
      Python 2.6+ with argparse
      matplotlib
   
    ~Â Usage
      
      plotser.py [OPTION]... <device>
      
      optional arguments:
        -b, --baudrate BAUD     serial baud rate (default: 9600)

